snippet.title: Let's Play: Bionic Commando Rearmed 2 [PS3][HD]
snippet.description:
It's time for another GameAnyone exclusive! This time, it's Bionic Commando Rearmed 2, sequel to Bionic Commando Rearmed.

This game has some nice additions, and some not-so-nice ones, but overall, it's shaping up to be quite a game!

See the rest at:
http://www.gameanyone.com/game/PS3/8884.html
